<ul style="list-style-type:disc">
    <li><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">范式的英文名称是</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"> Normal Form
            </span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">，简称</span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"> NF </span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">。它是英国人</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"> E.F.Codd </span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">在上个世纪</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">70</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">年代提出关系数据库模型后总结出来的。范式是关系数据库理论的基础，也是我们在设计数据库结构过程中所要遵循的规则和指导方法。</span></span>
    </li>
</ul>
<p><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;"><span
                style="color:black">&nbsp;</span></span></span></p>
<ul style="list-style-type:disc">
    <li><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">设计数据库时，遵从不同的规范要求，设计出合理的关系型数据库，这些不同的规范要求被称为不同的范式，各种范式呈递次规范，越高的范式数据库冗余越小。要想设计一个结构合理的关系型数据库，必须满足一定的范式。</span></span>
        <span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">规范化的目的是使结构更合理，消除存储异常，使数据冗余尽量小。便于插入、删除和更新数据</span></span>
    </li>
</ul>
<p><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;"><span
                style="color:black">&nbsp;</span></span></span></p>
<p style="margin-left: 80px;"><img
        src="data:image/png;base64,">
</p>
<p><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">&nbsp;</span></span></p>
<ul style="list-style-type:disc">
    <li><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">目前关系型数据库有六种常见范式：</span></span>
        <ul style="list-style-type:disc">
            <li><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                        style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">第一范式（</span></span><span
                    style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">1NF</span></span><span
                    style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">）</span></span>
            </li>
            <li><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                        style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">第二范式（</span></span><span
                    style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">2NF</span></span><span
                    style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">）</span></span>
            </li>
            <li><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                        style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">第三范式（</span></span><span
                    style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">3NF</span></span><span
                    style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">）</span></span>
            </li>
            <li><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                        style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">巴斯</span></span><span
                    style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">-</span></span><span
                    style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                        style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">科德范式（</span></span><span
                    style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">BCNF</span></span><span
                    style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">）</span></span>
            </li>
            <li><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                        style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">第四范式</span></span><span
                    style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">(4NF</span></span><span
                    style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">）</span></span>
            </li>
            <li><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                        style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">第五范式（</span></span><span
                    style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">5NF</span></span><span
                    style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                        style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">，又称完美范式）</span></span></li>
        </ul>
    </li>
</ul>
<p><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;"><span
                style="color:black">&nbsp;</span></span></span></p>
<ul style="list-style-type:disc">
    <li><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">满足最低要求的范式是第一范式（</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">1NF</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">）。在第一范式的基础上进一步满足更多规范要求的称为第二范式（</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">2NF</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">），其余范式以次类推</span></span>
    </li>
</ul>
<p><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"><span
                style="color:black">&nbsp;</span></span></span></p>
<ul style="list-style-type:disc">
    <li><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">在设计数据库时，会参考范式要求来做，但是并不是说遵循的范式等级越高越好，范式过高虽然具有对数据关系有更好的约束性，但是也会导致表之间的关系更加繁琐，从而导致每次操作的表会变多，数据库性能下降。通常，在关系型数据库设计中，最高也就遵循到</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"> BCNF </span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">，普遍还是</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"> 3NF</span></span></li>
</ul>
<p style="margin-left:36px"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"><span
                style="color:black">&nbsp;</span></span></span></p>
<p style="margin-left:36px"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"><span
                style="color:black">&nbsp;</span></span></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size:13.5pt"><span style="color:black"><strong><span
                    style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">第一范式（</span></strong><strong><span
                    style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">1</span></strong><strong><span
                    style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">NF</span></strong><strong><span
                    style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">）</span></strong></span></span></p>
<ol style="list-style-type:decimal">
    <li value="1"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">字段值具有原子性，不能再分（所有关系型数据库系统都满足第一范式）</span></span></li>
</ol>

<p><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">&nbsp;</span></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size:13.5pt"><strong><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">第二范式（</span></strong><strong><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">2</span></strong><strong><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">NF</span></strong><strong><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">）</span></strong></span></p>
<ul style="list-style-type:disc">
    <li><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">满足 </span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">1</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">NF </span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">的前提下，减少数据冗余，消除了非主键字段对主键的部分依赖</span></span></li>
</ul>
<p><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">&nbsp;</span></span></p>
<ul style="list-style-type:disc">
    <li><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">必须有主键，非主键字段都必须完全依赖于主键，而不能部分依赖主键</span></span></li>
</ul>
<p><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">&nbsp;</span></span></p>
<ul style="list-style-type:disc">
    <li><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">也就是说在一个数据库表中，一个表中只能保存一种数据，不可以把多种数据保存在同一张数据库表中，应当进行拆表</span></span>
    </li>
</ul>
<p><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">&nbsp;</span></span></p>
<ul style="list-style-type:disc">
    <li><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">下面的表中存在主键，满足</span></span> <span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">1NF </span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">，</span></span><span

            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">] </span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">和</span></span> <span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">[</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">教师姓名</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">] </span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">不完全依赖于</span></span> <span

<p><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">&nbsp;</span></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">&nbsp;</span></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size:13.5pt"><strong><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">第三范式（</span></strong><strong><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">3</span></strong><strong><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">NF</span></strong><strong><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">）</span></strong></span></p>
<ul style="list-style-type:disc">
    <li><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">满足</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"> 2NF </span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">的前提下，消除非主属性之间的传递依赖</span></span></li>
</ul>
<p style="margin-left: 80px;"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
            style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">「</span> <span
            style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">主键</span> <span
            style="font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;">→</span> <span
            style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">非主属性</span><span
            style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"> !</span><span
            style="font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;">→</span> <span
            style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">？」</span></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">&nbsp;</span></span></p>
<ul style="list-style-type:disc">
    <li><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">非主键外的字段必须互不依赖，即需要确保数据表中的每一列数据都和主键直接相关，而不能间接相关，不出现其他表的非主键属性</span></span>
    </li>
</ul>
<p><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">&nbsp;</span></span></p>
<ul style="list-style-type:disc">
    <li><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">以下的表中所有字段依赖于</span></span> <span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">[</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">学号</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">] </span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">，符合</span></span> <span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">2NF </span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">，但是从</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;"> [</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">班级编号</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">] </span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">可以得到</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;"> [</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">班级名称</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">]</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">，存在间接相关，不符合</span></span>
        <span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">3NF </span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">，且</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;"> [</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">班级编号</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">] </span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">和</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;"> [</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">班级名称</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">] </span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">都是班级表的属性，不属于学生表，应当单独拆分成一张表，用外键进行关联</span></span>
    </li>
</ul>

<p><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">&nbsp;</span></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">&nbsp;</span></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">&nbsp;</span></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size:13.5pt"><span
            style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;"><strong>反三范式</strong></span></span></p>
<ul style="list-style-type:disc">
    <li><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">范式的优点是明显的，它避免了大量的数据冗余，节省了存储空间，保持了数据的一致性。范式化的表通常更小，可以更好地放在内存里，所以执行操作会更快。</span></span>
    </li>
</ul>
<p><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">&nbsp;</span></span></p>
<ul style="list-style-type:disc">
    <li><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">那么是不是只要把所有的表都规范为</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"> 3NF</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">后，数据库的设计就是最优的呢？这可不一定。范式越高意味着表的划分更细，一个数据库中需要的表也就越多，用户不得不将原本相关联的数据分摊到多个表中。稍微复杂一些的查询语句在符合范式的数据库上都可能需要至少一次关联，也许更多，这不但代价昂贵，也可能使一些索引策略无效。</span></span>
    </li>
</ul>
<p><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">&nbsp;</span></span></p>
<ul style="list-style-type:disc">
    <li><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">所以我们在进行数据库设计时，并不会完全按照范式要求来做，有时候也会进行反范式设计。通过增加冗余或重复的数据来提高数据库的读性能，减少关联查询时，</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">join </span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">表的次数</span></span></li>
</ul>
<p><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">&nbsp;</span></span></p>
<ul style="list-style-type:disc">
    <li><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">是一种空间换时间的优化手段。因为我们遵循业务优先原则，可以通过在表中增加冗余字段来提高数据库的读性能</span></span>
    </li>
</ul>
<p><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">&nbsp;</span></span></p>
<ul style="list-style-type:disc">
    <li><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">当冗余信息有价值或者能大幅度提高查询效率的时候，我们才会采用反范式化进行优化</span></span>
    </li>
</ul>
<p><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">&nbsp;</span></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">&nbsp;</span></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">&nbsp;</span></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size:13.5pt"><strong><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;"><span
                    style="color:black">巴斯</span></span></strong><strong><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"><span style="color:black"> /
                </span></span></strong><strong><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">鲍依斯</span></strong><strong><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"><span
                    style="color:black">-</span></span></strong><strong><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;"><span style="color:black">科德</span></span></strong>
        <strong><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;"><span
                    style="color:black">范式（</span></span></strong><strong><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"><span
                    style="color:black">BCNF</span></span></strong><strong><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;"><span
                    style="color:black">）</span></span></strong></span></p>
<ul style="list-style-type:disc">
    <li><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">BCNF</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">是在第三范式的基础上，进一步消除了主属性对主键</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;"> / </span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">候选键的部分和传递函数依赖</span></span></li>
</ul>
<p><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">&nbsp;</span></span></p>
<ul style="list-style-type:disc">
    <li><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">消除部分函数依赖</span></span>
    </li>
</ul>
<p><span style="font-size:12.0pt">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <span
            style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">「</span> <span
            style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">候选键</span><span
            style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">[A, B]&nbsp; </span><span
            style="font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;">→</span> <span
            style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">主属性</span><span
            style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">D </span><span
            style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">」，「</span> <span
            style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">主属性</span><span
            style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">A / B !</span><span
            style="font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;">→</span> <span
            style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">主属性</span><span
            style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">D </span><span
            style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">」</span></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">&nbsp;</span></span></p>
<ul style="list-style-type:disc">
    <li><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">消除传递函数依赖</span></span>
    </li>
</ul>
<p><span style="font-size:12.0pt">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <span
            style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">「</span> <span
            style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">候选键</span><span
            style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"> [A, B]&nbsp; </span><span
            style="font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;">→</span> <span
            style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">主属性</span><span
            style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">C !</span><span
            style="font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;">→</span> <span
            style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">主属性</span><span
            style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">D </span><span
            style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">」</span></span></p>

<ul style="list-style-type:disc">
    <li><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">关系模式</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">R</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">＜</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">U</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">，</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">F</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">＞</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Cambria Math&quot;">∈</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">1NF</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">，如果对于</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">R</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">的每个非平凡多值依赖</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">X</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;">→→</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">Y</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">（</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">Y </span></span>⊈&nbsp;<span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">X</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">），</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">X</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">都含有侯选码，则</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">R</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Cambria Math&quot;">∈</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">4NF</span><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">。</span></span></li>
</ul>
<p><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">&nbsp;</span></span></p>
<ul style="list-style-type:disc">
    <li><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">4NF</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">就是限制关系模式的属性之间不允许有非平凡且非函数依赖的多值依赖。因为根据定义，对于每一个非平凡的多值依赖</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">X</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;">→→</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">Y</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">（</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">Y </span></span>⊈&nbsp;<span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">X</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">），</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">X</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">都含有侯选码，于是当然</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">X</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;">→</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">Y</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">，所以</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">4NF</span><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">所允许的非平凡多值依赖实际上是函数依赖。</span></span></li>
</ul>
